      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Jul 2022 16:44:50 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/40_configure_network/30_telegraf_configuration.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;1-to-monitor-your-nodes-in-cypress-dashboard-please-change-the-influxdb-configuration-as-below&#34;&gt;1. To monitor your nodes in Cypress Dashboard, please change the influxdb configuration as below:&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;1-for-both-cn-and-pn&#34;&gt;1) For both CN and PN,&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ grep -A2 &amp;#34;influxdb&amp;#34; /etc/telegraf/telegraf.d/klaytn.conf&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;[[outputs.influxdb]]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;urls = [ &amp;#34;http://13.209.53.161:45560&amp;#34; ]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;database = &amp;#34;klaytn_cypress&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;2-only-for-cn&#34;&gt;2) Only for CN,&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Change the interval time of Telegraf agent from 10s to 1s.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ cat /etc/telegraf/telegraf.conf | grep -v &amp;#39;^\s*$\|^\s*\#&amp;#39; | grep interval&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;interval = &amp;#34;1s&amp;#34;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;round_interval = true&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;flush_interval = &amp;#34;1s&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;If you finish this step, please click the next button &lt;code&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; on the right side of this page.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Change log level</title>
      <link>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/50_start_services/60_change_log_level.html</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:43:05 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/50_start_services/60_change_log_level.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;6-change-log-level&#34;&gt;6. Change log level&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo kcn attach --exec debug.verbosity(1) DATA_DIR/klay.ipc&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sudo kcn attach --exec debug.vmodule(&amp;#34;blockchain=3&amp;#34;) DATA_DIR/klay.ipc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;If you finish this step, please click the next button &lt;code&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; on the right side of this page.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Datadog Configuration</title>
      <link>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/40_configure_network/40_datadog_configuration.html</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Jul 2022 15:33:50 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>/klaytn-cypress-setup-workshop/40_configure_network/40_datadog_configuration.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;2-for-additional-monitoring-we-are-planning-to-use-datadog-as-well-please-follow-this-step-for-datadog-installation&#34;&gt;2. For additional monitoring, we are planning to use Datadog as well. Please follow this step for Datadog installation.&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;1-for-cn&#34;&gt;1) For CN,&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ cat &lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;EOF&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt; dd_vars&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export DD_API_KEY=DATADOG API KEY&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export NETWORK=cypress&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export NODE_NAME=&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;cco_name&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;-cn-01&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export NODE_TYPE=cn &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export INSTANCE=cn &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export LOG_DIR=&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;your_klaytn_home_path&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;/kcnd/log&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;EOF&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ source dd_vars&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ bash -c &amp;#34;$(curl -L https://raw.githubusercontent.com/klaytn/datadog-agent-install./main/install-datadog-agent.sh)&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;** DD_API_KEY will be shared with you by Slack DM.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;** Please use lowercase for NODE_NAME.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;** For example, &lt;code&gt;LOG_DIR = /data/kcnd/log or /data/kcnd/logs, NODE_NAME=cco_name-cn-01&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
